description_data.value: ** RESERVED ** This candidate has been reserved by an organization or individual that will use it when announcing a new security problem. When the candidate has been publicized, the details for this candidate will be provided.

descriptions.value: An arbitrary file upload vulnerability in the Add Student's Profile Picture function of Student Enrollment In PHP v1.0 allows attackers to execute arbitrary code via uploading a crafted PHP file.

Una vulnerabilidad de carga de archivos arbitrarios en la función Agregar imagen de perfil del estudiante de Student Enrollment In PHP v1.0 permite a los atacantes ejecutar código arbitrario cargando un archivo PHP manipulado.
